gov.nih.nlm.meme
Interface MEMEConstants

All Known Subinterfaces:
ClientConstants, DataSourceConstants, DataSourceConstants, ServerConstants, ServerConstants
All Known Implementing Classes:
MEMEException, MEMEToolkit, MIDServices
public interface MEMEConstants

This interface holds constants commonly used by MEME applications. Many of them represent names used in a properties file (like DEBUG).

Author:
MEME Group
